  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To establish the proof of concept that MEM 3454, used as add-on pharmacotherapy, is a safe
      and effective treatment in patients with cognitive impairment associated with schizophrenia
      (CIAS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
